<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>An applicant may seek Advanced Placement credit by submitting a transcript of previous grades and AP scores to the Registrar's Office.  PMC grants 4 credits for each AP score of 4 or 5. These credits count toward the degree, but do not fulfill distribution requirements or count toward the requirements of a major.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.pmc.edu/academic/catalog/" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
</p>

